de.dsa.hackathon2013.app

Class DSADiagnosticsActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • de.dsa.hackathon2013.app.DSADiagnosticsActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.dsa.hackathon2013.app.readertask.DiagnosticReaderFragment.VehicleValuesReaderTaskCallbacks

    public class DSADiagnosticsActivity
extends Activity
implements de.dsa.hackathon2013.app.readertask.DiagnosticReaderFragment.VehicleValuesReaderTaskCallbacks
    Main Activity for the Diagnostics Application. The Activity will display a list of values read from the vehicle. This operation is performed in a background thread and provides the activity with progress updates. The activity also has a menu action to allow the user to read new values from the vehicle.
